title: Michigan MIRIS Railroads
description: Railroads throughout the State of Michigan.  Data is edited through the forest compartment review process.  Original linework came from the MiRIS base maps which were digitized from the 1978 USGS Topographic Quadrangles.

title: Public Land Survey Sections
description: Survey sections and private claims for Michigan's Upper and Lower PeninsulasMore Metadata

title: Michigan DNR Managed Culverts
description: Point data for culvert locations. These culverts are managed through the DNR's forest inventory process.

title: Michigan DNR Managed Gates and Berms
description: Gates and Berms are managed through the DNR's forest inventory process.

title: DNR Visitor Centers
description: Points are extracted from the Citrix Facilities database.  Locations are derived from the latitude/longitude coordinates entered into the Facilities database.

title: Michigan DNR Managed Roads
description: State Forest Roads are from the Michigan Geographic Framework dataset version 9 with state forest roads added through the Department of Natural Resources' (DNR) forest inventory process.  This dataset is not complete at this time, but will have new roads added as the DNR continues its forest inventory process.

description:

title: DNR Agency Facilities
description: Points are extracted from the Citrix Facilities database.  Locations are derived from the latitude/longitude coordinates entered into the Facilities database.

title: Michigan DNR Managed Bridges
description: Point data for bridge locations, includes vehicular and pedestrian bridges on road networks and recreational trails. These bridges are updated through the DNR's forest inventory and trails management processes.

title: DNR Forest Management Unit Office
description:
Feature

title: Michigan Utility Lines
description: Pipelines, Powerlines, and Underground Cable features.  Data is edited through the forest compartment review process.  Original linework came from 1978 MiRIS base maps.
